beer.beer_description:
Colour — Rich Amber
Brewed with a combination of pale malt and ale malt from one of the worlds best malteries, with the addition of caramel malts and tonnes (and we mean tonnes) of hops! A combination of American and Aussie hops making up the blend. With a few secret Aussie ingredients to finish off, including dried finger lime peel for a fantastic citrusy zing. Expect great balance between malts, hops and spices.
